you never know.

00:15.282 --> 00:16.848
Steven!

00:16.851 --> 00:19.618
Reuniting with my friend
and old co-star steven yeun.

00:19.686 --> 00:21.620
For a three-day ride
around san francisco...

00:21.688 --> 00:23.689
