to be doing in this moment.

00:26.793 --> 00:28.293
So sorry you got
your head blown off.

00:28.361 --> 00:30.001
Yeah. But I'm back.
I'm back with my dude.

00:32.098 --> 00:34.633
Freaks and outcasts have long
ruled the golden gate city.

00:36.236 --> 00:38.170
It's where fringe music
steps out of the shadows.

00:38.238 --> 00:39.872
We were just the weirdo band.

00:39.940 --> 00:42.474
It's a place where people push
back against convention...

00:42.542 --> 00:44.976
- Is that wrong?
- It's so wrong that it's right.

00:45.045 --> 00:47.813
And every so often
revolutionize the world.

00:47.881 --> 00:48.881
All right. Let's go.

00:52.586 --> 00:55.921
All right, hit it!

00:55.989 --> 00:58.356
Here we go! Yeah, baby!

01:00.294 --> 01:02.361
That was crazy!

