He's a skateboarding legend.

01:51.211 --> 01:53.712
And a highly acclaimed
custom-bike builder.

01:53.780 --> 01:55.147
A mutual friend hooked us up.

01:55.215 --> 01:57.883
For an early morning
ride around the city.

01:57.885 --> 01:59.395
Then I'm going to go
meet my friend steven,

01:59.419 --> 02:02.787
