02:02.856 --> 02:04.296
This is a pano...
Panorama situation.

02:04.324 --> 02:06.124
Yeah, this is a pano. For sure.

02:06.127 --> 02:08.827
In oakland, you say, "the best
thing about san francisco."

02:08.829 --> 02:10.429
Is the view of it from oakland."

02:10.497 --> 02:11.897
yeah.

02:11.965 --> 02:13.365
Let's get out of here.
