03:33.180 --> 03:34.913
Over the next three days,

03:34.915 --> 03:36.515
I'll re-explore this city.

03:36.583 --> 03:38.127
Before cruising
the pacific coast highway.

03:38.151 --> 03:40.518
Into la honda.

03:40.521 --> 03:42.788
After a stop in wine country,

03:42.856 --> 03:44.656
I'll ride to oakland
to meet one of the most.

03:44.725 --> 03:47.425
Notorious motorcycle clubs
in the country.

03:49.163 --> 03:50.528
See you in two days.
We'll do oakland.

03:50.531 --> 03:52.497
Yeah. Let's do it.

03:52.565 --> 03:54.399
Right now it's time
to part ways with max.

03:54.468 --> 03:55.878
We're gonna meet up
again in a few days.

03:55.902 --> 03:57.636
To explore
the streets of oakland.

