'cause you can ride every day.

07:48.668 --> 07:50.379
Yeah. So tell me about
the thing that you guys do.

07:50.403 --> 07:51.581
- You guys...
- Dirtbag challenge?

07:51.605 --> 07:53.038
Dirtbag...
Dirtbag challenge, yeah.

07:53.106 --> 07:55.306
Yeah, I started that
with, three friends,

07:55.309 --> 07:57.219
Talking smack amongst us,
who could build a bike.

07:57.243 --> 07:58.688
For the cheapest
the quickest, you know?

07:58.712 --> 08:00.645
We made trophies and stuff,
you know, and...

08:00.647 --> 08:02.480
But there's no money
or anything like that.

08:02.483 --> 08:06.150
It's just, for the glory. Yeah.

08:12.259 --> 08:14.059
So this is my bike,
one of my bikes.

08:14.127 --> 08:16.461
Been through an engine and
crashed it a few times and...

08:16.529 --> 08:17.962
I built that.

