all know each other?

08:38.952 --> 08:41.686
- We're all dirtbags.
- Yeah, I know...

08:41.688 --> 08:43.221
- Met at the dirtbag.
- Yeah.

08:43.222 --> 08:46.124
Except for satan,
who is my shopmate, so...

08:46.192 --> 08:48.426
Satan? Why do they call
you satan? Do I...

08:48.495 --> 08:50.172
Should I... should I even ask?
He earned - he earned that.

08:50.196 --> 08:52.007
- I'm trying to figure it out.
- He earned that name.

08:52.031 --> 08:53.965
That's a story for another time.

08:54.033 --> 08:55.811
- When there are no cameras recording us.
- Yeah.

08:55.835 --> 08:57.536
It's such a sense of community.

08:57.604 --> 08:58.970
I mean, like, you can see all
the little communities here,

08:58.972 --> 09:00.449
Like, but, I mean,
san francisco in general.

09:00.473 --> 09:01.840
Has been always a place that,

09:01.908 --> 09:03.686
Like, political movements and...
Absolutely.

09:03.710 --> 09:05.110
Artists who speak their mind.

09:05.178 --> 09:06.911
Do you feel, like,
a collective, like,

09:06.980 --> 09:08.813
Everybody agrees
and understands, like,

09:08.881 --> 09:12.384
"hey, you just do your thing,
and I'm gonna do my thing"?

