or whatever to write code...

09:31.538 --> 09:33.672
They've got so much money,
they can do what they want.

09:33.740 --> 09:35.840
It's like wall street guys.
I mean... Yeah.

09:35.908 --> 09:37.186
Real-estate agents.
They're just...

09:37.210 --> 09:38.376
They're milking the beast.

09:38.444 --> 09:40.511
- Yeah. That's crazy.
- Right?

09:40.580 --> 09:42.880
Here's the thing is none of us
have any money at all. Yeah.

09:42.883 --> 09:46.718
Like, we're all broke as
but we don't care.

09:46.786 --> 09:49.520
