is made up of people like us.

09:49.589 --> 09:51.356
We live the kind
of lifestyle, you know,

09:51.424 --> 09:53.691
A lot of people
could only dream of.

09:53.760 --> 09:55.760
San francisco has
always been a refuge.

09:55.828 --> 09:58.029
For those outside
the mainstream,

09:58.097 --> 10:02.200
A place that prides itself on
social and economic diversity,

10:02.268 --> 10:03.835
And it's locals
like poll and his crew.

10:03.903 --> 10:05.403
